title: Seattle’s Spirit Award Live on KEXP out now 📺
Spirit Award - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Spirit Award performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded May 18, 2023

Songs:
Western Violence
Pushing Forward
Unlock the Door
Guilt and Shame

Daniel Lyon - Vocals, Guitar
Chris Jordan - Bass
Nate Louis - Drums

Bryce Barsten - Keyboards

Host: Cheryl Waters
